#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L10_ImageComposition
msgid "# Image Distributes Over Composition\n"
"\n"
"In Preimage World, you proved that preimage respects composition:\n"
"§0. Now you will prove the dual\n"
"result for images:\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
"Applying the composed function directly gives the same result as\n"
"applying §2 first, then applying §3 to the output.\n"
"\n"
"**The proof exercises nested destructuring**: The backward direction\n"
"requires destructuring TWO levels of image membership. If\n"
"§4, there exists §5 with §6, and\n"
"within that, there exists §7 with §8. The pattern\n"
"§9 handles both levels at once.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. §10 then §11\n"
"2. **Forward**: Destructure §12 membership, then construct\n"
"   nested image membership in §13\n"
"3. **Backward**: Nested destructuring, then construct §14\n"
"   membership directly"
msgstr ""

