msgid "# Boss: Integration Challenge\n"
"\n"
"This boss combines techniques from across Injective World into a single\n"
"proof:\n"
"\n"
"- The canonical §0 shape (Levels 1–2)\n"
"- Extracting an explicit equation with §1 (Levels 1–2)\n"
"- Left-inverse instantiation: §2 (Level 7)\n"
