#: Game.Levels.InjectiveWorld.L07_LeftInverse
msgid "You proved that left inverses imply injectivity!\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"**The chain of equalities**: The proof establishes\n"
"§1, where:\n"
"- The first §2 comes from §3 (left inverse property)\n"
"- The middle §4 comes from §5 (the injectivity assumption §6)\n"
"- The last §7 comes from §8 (left inverse property again)\n"
"\n"
"**Why left inverses force injectivity**: A left inverse §9 \"remembers\"\n"
"the original input. Since §10 always recovers §11, no\n"
"information can be lost by applying §12. If two inputs gave the\n"
"same output, §13 could not recover both — contradiction.\n"
"\n"
