msgid "# Preimages: Pulling Sets Back Through Functions\n"
"\n"
"You have mastered sets, subsets, and set operations. Now you will see\n"
"how **functions** interact with sets.\n"
"\n"
"Given a function §0 and a set §1 (a set of\n"
"**outputs**), the **preimage** of §2 under §3 is the set of all\n"
