#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L06_ImageMonotonicity
msgid "# Image Is Monotone\n"
"\n"
"If §0, then §1. In words: a bigger input set\n"
"produces a bigger output set. This is **monotonicity** of image.\n"
"\n"
"Why? If §2, there exists §3 with §4. Since\n"
"§5, we have §6. So the SAME witness §7 proves §8.\n"
"\n"
"This is your first abstract image proof. It is also your first\n"
"chance to use §9 on a subset proof. The subset goal\n"
"§10 means §11, so\n"
"§12 destructures the image membership.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. §13 -- introduce §14 and destructure\n"
"2. Construct the new image membership using the SAME witness §15"
msgstr ""

