#: Game.Levels.IndexedOpsWorld.L11_CartesianProduct
msgid "# Cartesian Products of Sets\n"
"\n"
"The **cartesian product** §0 of two sets §1 and\n"
"§2 is the set of all pairs §3 with §4 and §5:\n"
"\n"
"§6\n"
"\n"
"This is yet another set operation that reduces to a logical connective —\n"
"this time §7, just like §8. The difference is that §9 combines\n"
"two sets of the **same** type, while §10 combines sets of\n"
"**different** types into a set of pairs.\n"
"\n"
"**New tool**: §11 converts §12 into\n"
"§13. After that, use §14 to split the\n"
"conjunction, just like with §15.\n"
"\n"
"**Notation**: The §16 superscript in §17 stands for \"set\". It\n"
