"§25 shows equality fails. The outputs §26\n"
"and §27 appear in every §28 via DIFFERENT witnesses, but no\n"
"single witness belongs to every §29.\n"
"\n"
"**The pattern**: This is the indexed version of the same phenomenon:\n"
"\n"
"| Operation | Preimage | Image |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Binary §30 | = | only \\\\subseteq |\n"
"| Indexed §31 | = | only \\\\subseteq |\n"
"| Binary §32 | = | = |\n"
"| Indexed §33 | = | = |\n"
"\n"
"The next level proves the indexed union case — the §34 in the last\n"
"row. Image preserves ALL unions (binary and indexed) as equalities,\n"
"but only \\\\subseteq for intersections.\n"
"\n"
"The library name is §35."
