"\n"
"Here is the critical asymmetry between image and preimage.\n"
"Preimage preserves intersection as an EQUALITY:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"For image, we only get a SUBSET:\n"
"\n"
"§1\n"
"\n"
