#: Game.Levels.InjectiveWorld.L08_Boss
msgid "Congratulations — you completed **Injective World**!\n"
"\n"
"## What You Learned\n"
"\n"
"**The canonical injectivity proof**:\n"
"§0\n"
"Every injectivity proof starts this way. What follows depends on the\n"
"setting:\n"
"- **Arithmetic**: extract the equation (§1), then §2\n"
"- **Composition**: chain §3 then §4\n"
"- **Extraction**: §5, then §6 + §7\n"
"- **Left inverse**: instantiate §8 and §9, then rewrite\n"
"\n"
"**Disproving injectivity**: Find two distinct inputs with the same\n"
"output, apply injectivity to get a false equation, derive contradiction.\n"
"\n"
"**Composition rules**:\n"
"| Hypothesis | Conclusion |\n"
"|---|---|\n"
"| §10, §11 | §12 |\n"
"| §13 | §14 |\n"
"| §15 | §16 |\n"
"| §17 | §18 — **FALSE** |\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: In Surjective World, you will learn the dual\n"
"story. The roles reverse in a surprising way: §19\n"
"implies §20 (the INNER function), but §21\n"
"implies §22 (the OUTER function!). This asymmetry — injection\n"
"tests the inner factor, surjection tests the outer factor — is one of\n"
"the deepest patterns in function theory."
msgstr ""

