#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L12_ImageUnivRange
msgid "# Connecting Image and Range\n"
"\n"
"In Level 11, you learned that §0 is the set of all outputs\n"
"of §1. There is a direct connection to image: the range IS the image\n"
"of the universal set §2 (the set of ALL inputs):\n"
