#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L01_ImageMembership
msgid "# Images: Pushing Sets Forward Through Functions\n"
"\n"
"In Preimage World, you pulled sets **backward** through functions:\n"
"§0 meant §1 -- just function application.\n"
"\n"
"Now you will push sets **forward**. The **image** of a set §2\n"
"under §3 is:\n"
"\n"
"§4\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, this is written §5 (type §6). The membership rule is:\n"
"\n"
"§7\n"
"\n"
"This is §8. Notice the **existential**: to prove something\n"
"is in the image, you must **exhibit a witness** -- a specific input §9\n"
"in §10 that maps to §11. This is fundamentally different from preimage,\n"
"which had no existential.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that 4 is in the image of the set of natural numbers\n"
"less than 5, under the function §12.\n"
"\n"
"The witness is §13, because §14 (since §15) and §16.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. §17 -- provide the witness\n"
"2. §18 -- split the conjunction (membership + equation)\n"
"3. Prove §19 with §20 and §21\n"
"4. Prove §22 with §23"
msgstr ""

