#: Game.Levels.IndexedOpsWorld.L10_VacuousUnion
msgid "# The Dual: Union over Nothing\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you proved the surprising fact that intersecting\n"
"over an empty family gives §0 — because the condition\n"
"§1 is vacuously true when there are no indices.\n"
