#: Game.Levels.IndexedOpsWorld.L03_IInterSubset
msgid "# Using §0 in a Hypothesis\n"
"\n"
"In the previous level, you used §1 on the **goal**\n"
"to convert §2 into §3. But §4 is\n"
"just as useful on a **hypothesis**.\n"
"\n"
"If you know §5, then §6\n"
"converts §7 to §8. After that, you can\n"
"**specialize** it to any particular index by writing §9.\n"
"\n"
"This is the fundamental pattern for *using* an indexed intersection:\n"
"unwrap the §10, then apply it to the index you need.\n"
"\n"
