#: Game.Levels.SubsetWorld.L18_Boss
msgid "Congratulations — you have completed **Subset World**!\n"
"\n"
"Here is your toolkit:\n"
"\n"
"| Concept | Lean | Proof move |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| Subset §0 | §1 | §2 then show §3 |\n"
"| Reflexivity §4 | identity | §5 |\n"
"| §6 | vacuously true | §7 |\n"
"| §8 | trivially true | §9 |\n"
"| Transitivity | §10 | chain with §11 or function application |\n"
"| Set equality via ext | §12 | §13 |\n"
"| Set equality via antisymm | §14 | §15 |\n"
