"| Dot projection | §22, §23 | extract components of §24 or §25 |\n"
"\n"
"The §26 relation is a **partial order** on sets: it is reflexive\n"
"(Level 3), transitive (Level 8), and antisymmetric (Level 14). The\n"
"strict variant §27 (proper subset, Level 15) excludes equality.\n"
"\n"
"In the next world, you will learn about **set operations**: union (§28),\n"
"intersection (§29), complement (§30), and difference (§31intro x hx` proof\n"
"pattern you mastered here will be the foundation for every one of\n"
