#: Game.Levels.ImageWorld.L07_ImageUnion
msgid "# Image Distributes Over Union\n"
"\n"
"Here is the first major structural result for images:\n"
"\n"
"§0\n"
"\n"
"Why does this work? Image involves §1, and existentials distribute\n"
"over disjunction. If §2, there exists §3\n"
"with §4. Since §5, the SAME witness §6 places\n"
"§7 in either §8 or §9.\n"
"\n"
"Compare with preimage: §10 also\n"
"held, because §11 passes through function application. Image preserves\n"
"union for a different reason: §12 distributes over §13.\n"
"\n"
"**Proof plan**:\n"
"1. §14 then §15 -- standard set equality structure\n"
"2. **Forward**: destructure image of union, case-split on membership,\n"
"   place the witness in the correct image\n"
"3. **Backward**: case-split on the union of images, destructure each\n"
"   case, repackage with union membership"
msgstr ""

